name: Jetpack Doggo
description:
Very small 2D game where you play as the Jetpack Doggo, trying to avoid the birbs coming your way. You earn score based on how many birbs you can get past.

I made this game during my spare-time over the course of a week. Art provided by my partner. If you want to influence development of future games developed by me, join the team as a tester or just want to hang around, there is a discord server:
https://discord.gg/jkzp3wZQac

Feedback is much appreciated!
